{"msg":{"list":[{"title":null,"userName":"罗磊","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoCv1vtHZcnrZ8l6iaZ4oRlSs5kqGtyCASniaAibfjEoViaYNyXiaLDhzTeBbYQaOicj2oK3rW78yXrNtHr/0","content":"站不住脚。婚姻是有婚姻法，受法律保护。性行为属于个人行为。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8957,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492767554000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Rane","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98UZYfXiaDTkrtVMibw9sJy3fMk3YrMYVa5IouXAzQuI8mxyKrACuibLcUziaPdxoTzCB0x1kIgq3QNDrbaTcuIUbicfD/0","content":"同意同性行为不代表同意了重婚，乱伦，通奸等等，就像同意异性性行为不代表同意出轨，群交等行为一样，两者之间没有必然的联系。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8884,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492752196000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"青青枣实～","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/UPj0egwhddG46evSjhoopsDOglJ7YDNJTysd8ZXpLppVibia3UjtV3rAsibHvE3RxfbTrxP1BIFxdRpR6LrLPUahp0GibZUNPGy6/0","content":"<div>1. 脱离前提条件</div><div>(1)分析</div><div>你有权在自己的房间里发生双方同意的同性性行为，前提条件是：双方处于未婚状态、无婚姻关系。而重婚代表着已建立起了婚姻关系，不满足前提条件，无法推出结论。</div><div><br></div><div>(2)举例</div><div>假如我没有水果，就可以得到圈圈送的苹果。若缺少前提条件-我没有水果，就推不结论。即：我有了香蕉，推不出圈圈还送了一箱苹果给我。</div><div><br></div><div>2. 偷换概念</div><div>分析：即便有权多婚，肯定的是和多个人结婚这一事件，强调的数量可以大于1，并未肯定多婚的对象为＊＊，推不出有权乱伦。</div><div>同样的，有权多婚推有权通奸，前者肯定数量，后者强调对象。偷换话题的概念。例如：有权吃多个苹果，推不出可以吃别人家的苹果。</div><div><br></div><div>3. 部分推不出整体</div><div>即便有权乱伦、通奸，有部分权利不能推出有所有权利。比如：我有苹果、香蕉，推不出我有所有的水果。</div><div><br></div><div><br></div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8883,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492752147000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"梦想家杨小彤同学","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"htt